task.summary: Potential fix for SELinux on newer android versions.

- Moved screenshot to a middleman to accommodate requesting for permission. - Changed to higher compile version. - Changed default theme to light mode and changed icons on the first page to black from white. - Changed manifest version. - Added gradle dependency for the app combat library. - Removed unnecessary files from git.

MESSAGE.value: Potential fix for SELinux on newer android versions.

- Moved screenshot to a middleman to accommodate requesting for permission. - Changed to higher compile version. - Changed default theme to light mode and changed icons on the first page to black from white. - Changed manifest version. - Added gradle dependency for the app combat library. - Removed unnecessary files from git.

option.name: LAST_COMMIT_MESSAGE
option.value: - Decreased min android version.
